var timeIntervals = {
    millisecond: 1,
    second: 1e3,
    minute: 6e4,
    hour: 36e5,
    day: 864e5,
    week: 6048e5,
    month: 2592e6,
    quarter: 7776e6,
    year: 31536e6
};
export function toMilliseconds(value) {
    return timeIntervals[value]
}
